\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">，</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">品牌的价值</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">；</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">品牌与商标的关系</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">、</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">品牌与营销的关系﹑品牌与产品的</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">关系</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">、</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">品牌与</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">消费</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">者的关系</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">、</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">品牌定位与个性形象塑造﹑品牌策略﹑品牌与</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">公关</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">、</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">品牌网络传播及品牌整合传播</font></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'方正楷体简体\';\"><font face=\"方正楷体简体\">；</font></span></span><span st